text: Cylicocyclus nassatus is a very common species of cyathostomin, which are important intestinal parasites of horses. Cyathostomins, including C. nassatus, are nematodes. == References == == External links == * INPN Category:Strongylida Category:Parasitic nematodes of mammals Category:Parasites of equines Category:Veterinary helminthology Category:Nematodes described in 1900
title: Cylicocyclus nassatus
